    <item>
      <title>亚马逊不断膨胀的现金储备为派息创造了条件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/amazon-s-amzn-swelling-cash-pile-makes-conditions-ripe-for-dividend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司 (Amazon.com Inc.) 的现金储备预计今年将超过 1000 亿美元，这对于该公司与其他大型股公司一样向股东返还现金（包括可能打破股息限制）而言，是前所未有的有利条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/amazon-s-amzn-swelling-cash-pile-makes-conditions-ripe-for-dividend</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:23:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰因通胀加速而结束降息周期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/ukraine-ends-run-of-interest-rate-cuts-as-inflation-accelerates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀加速上升，乌克兰决策者发出信号称明年才可能恢复宽松政策，因此乌克兰停止了三次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/ukraine-ends-run-of-interest-rate-cuts-as-inflation-accelerates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国公司在中国受到热烈欢迎，但不确定是否受欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-firms-get-warm-welcome-in-china-but-unsure-if-they-re-wanted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周访问中国的美国企业高管有机会与习近平政府的高级官员会面，但他们在北京对外国投资的开放程度方面却收到了矛盾的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-firms-get-warm-welcome-in-china-but-unsure-if-they-re-wanted</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 11:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员押注降息在即，美国国债引领全球债券市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-treasuries-lead-global-bond-rally-as-haven-demand-picks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济放缓迹象和近期股市暴跌引发要求美联储加快降息的呼声，美国债券价格大幅上涨，进一步刺激了对收益率曲线趋陡的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-treasuries-lead-global-bond-rally-as-haven-demand-picks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 08:24:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>流媒体收入下降，环球音乐收入下跌 30%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/universal-sinks-30-after-subscription-growth-misses-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[环球音乐集团 (Universal Music Group NV) 的订阅和流媒体收入增长令投资者失望，其股价一度下跌 30%，为该公司首次公开募股以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/universal-sinks-30-after-subscription-growth-misses-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:52:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市在最繁忙的报告日受到疲软收益的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/european-stocks-slide-on-glum-earnings-in-season-s-busiest-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受开云集团 (Kering SA) 和雀巢公司 (Nestle SA) 等多家公司公布的业绩不佳影响，欧洲股市在企业财报季最繁忙的一天出现暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/european-stocks-slide-on-glum-earnings-in-season-s-busiest-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:14:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙提前大选导致法国商业信心下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/french-business-confidences-slumped-during-turbulent-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于企业考虑到提前选举带来的动荡使法国陷入不确定的政治未来，法国企业信心跌至新冠疫情以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/french-business-confidences-slumped-during-turbulent-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:45:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
